COLOR 15: PRINT : PRINT ""
1100 PRINT : COLOR 15: PRINT "": SLEEP 10: LET G = G + 5: GOTO LAND

2000 SCREEN 8: CLS : COLOR 6: PRINT "(ROYAL PALACE OF KING DON JUAN CARLOS IV, SATURN)"
IF VENUPROGRESS! > 1 THEN GOTO 2700
IF EARTPROGRESS! > 1 THEN GOTO 2600
IF MARSPROGRESS! > 1 THEN GOTO 2500
IF BOMB1! = 1 THEN GOTO 2400
